@NODE GIFTWARE "GIFTWARE"
As certain Mr.Huttenloher has released whole set of icons, fonts and 
WB-background patterns as shareware (Yes, MagicWB is C00L! :)), I decided to
change my release policy a bit, but as I'm not as cruel as he is (DM/US$20 is
a lot of money for a poor student...:( ), I've decided to choose GIFTWARE!
This means that if you like these fonts I demand that you should send me
something (preferably useful :)) like money, computers (A4000Ts, DEC Alphas
or CRAYs ;)), 24+bit gfx cards, 1GB HDs, commercial/(registered) shareware 
programs or something else... For those who will send something, I might send
some more fonts or/and diploma or something else (haven't decided yet...=;->).

@ENDNODE

