@NODE INSTALLATION "INSTALLATION"
As I haven't had time (or knowledge) to write Installer-script, you must
install these fonts manually. But as I believe that most Amiga owners know
how to copy files, this shouldn't be problem... :) So all you have to do is
to copy these fonts to somewhere in FONTS: (or add assign FONTS: to dir
where the fonts are located).

@ENDNODE

